      <title>由于每周较小的销售吸引了强劲的买盘，南非债券上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/south-africa-bonds-gain-as-smaller-weekly-sale-draws-strong-bids</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非本币债券周二成为新兴市场中表现最好的债券，此前政府缩减的每周债券发行规模吸引了投资者的强劲需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/south-africa-bonds-gain-as-smaller-weekly-sale-draws-strong-bids</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 11:50:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>制药商 Stada 称将与收购公司洽谈 80 亿欧元的出售事宜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/drugmaker-stada-said-to-talk-to-buyout-firms-in-8-billion-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Stada Arzneimittel AG 已开始与潜在买家进行谈判，这家德国仿制药制造商的所有者正在寻求可能的出售，该出售可能使该公司估值约为 80 亿欧元（合 87 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/drugmaker-stada-said-to-talk-to-buyout-firms-in-8-billion-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 11:49:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟加大对中国绿色科技风电调查的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/eu-ramps-up-pressure-on-china-s-green-tech-with-wind-power-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧盟努力将欧盟转变为绿色经济之际，欧盟加大了对中国清洁技术投资的压力，可能会排挤其当地供应商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/eu-ramps-up-pressure-on-china-s-green-tech-with-wind-power-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 11:47:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃里安认为有理由相信美国经济可能放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-09/el-erian-sees-reason-to-believe-us-economy-may-slow-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[剑桥大学皇后学院院长兼彭博社观点专栏作家穆罕默德·埃里安表示，企业对今年剩余时间的前景感到担忧，同时他解释了为什么预计美联储今年只会降息两次。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-09/el-erian-sees-reason-to-believe-us-economy-may-slow-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 11:46:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
