      <title>露得清 (Neutrogena) 将关闭洛杉矶办事处并裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/neutrogena-kvue-is-closing-its-la-office-and-laying-off-staff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着母公司 Kenvue Inc. 将业务整合到新泽西州，露得清 (Neutrogena) 将永久关闭其洛杉矶办事处。]]></description>
