    <item>
      <title>梅洛尼官员认为，随着增长的保持，意大利的债务将会上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/meloni-team-sees-italy-2024-growth-of-1-but-with-debt-rising</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据新的政府展望，意大利的债务负担将再次开始上升，该展望还坚称意大利经济将在 2024 年实现超出大多数预测的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/meloni-team-sees-italy-2024-growth-of-1-but-with-debt-rising</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 11:09:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>液化天然气转移至亚洲，欧洲天然气价格波动接近两周高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/european-gas-swings-near-two-week-high-as-supplies-on-ships-ease</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲天然气价格升至两周来最高水平，有迹象表明船只正在将燃料运往亚洲等其他市场，而挪威的供应因维护而受到限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/european-gas-swings-near-two-week-high-as-supplies-on-ships-ease</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 07:56:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黑石集团即将收购护肤品公司欧舒丹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/blackstone-said-to-near-buyout-of-skin-care-company-l-occitane</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，欧舒丹国际公司 (L&#39;Occitane International SA) 的亿万富翁所有者 Reinold Geiger 即将达成协议，在黑石公司 (Blackstone Inc.) 的资金帮助下将这家护肤品公司私有化，这可能会结束该公司在香港证券交易所 14 年的连续上市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/blackstone-said-to-near-buyout-of-skin-care-company-l-occitane</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 01:51:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
